   <mods:abstract>He has been required to make immediate arrangements for the cleaning of
            some small arms that were damaged by water, and this will, in part, be reimbursed by
            insurance. Suggestions as to the proper method of mounting cannon at Governor's Island.
            It would be wise for the legislature to make an annual appropriation for the procurement
            and maintenance of armament.</mods:abstract>
